msgid "Launch command preview"
msgstr "Pratinjau perintah peluncuran"

#. Common options
msgid "Performance overlay"
msgstr "Overlay performa"

msgid "Shows an in-game overlay with FPS, CPU/GPU usage, and temps."
msgstr ""
"Menampilkan overlay dalam permainan dengan FPS, penggunaan CPU/GPU, dan suhu."

msgid "Disable Steam Deck Mode"
msgstr "Nonaktifkan Mode Steam Deck"

msgid "Disables the Steam Deck-specific profile that some games use."
msgstr ""
"Menonaktifkan profil khusus Steam Deck yang digunakan oleh beberapa game."

msgid "Wayland"
msgstr "Wayland"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Runs the game natively on Wayland instead of through XWayland but it breaks "
"Steam Input and the Steam Overlay."
msgstr "Menjalankan game secara native di Wayland alih-alih melalui XWayland."

msgid "Common options"
msgstr "Opsi umum"

msgid "Quick toggles for the launch options people reach for most often."
msgstr "Pengalih cepat untuk opsi peluncuran yang paling sering digunakan."

#. Launch tools
msgid "HDR"
msgstr "HDR"

msgid "Outputs HDR colors if your display supports it."
msgstr "Menghasilkan warna HDR jika layar Anda mendukungnya."

msgid "None"
msgstr "Tidak ada"

msgid "Gamescope"
msgstr "Gamescope"

msgid "ScopeBuddy"
msgstr "ScopeBuddy"

msgid "Launch tools"
msgstr "Alat peluncuran"

msgid ""
"Choose one to configure FPS caps, resolution, and other display options."
msgstr ""
"Pilih salah satu untuk mengonfigurasi batas FPS, resolusi, dan opsi tampilan "
"lainnya."

#. GPU vendor options
msgid "Mesa Anti-Lag"
msgstr "Mesa Anti-Lag"

msgid "Reduces latency on supported AMD Mesa setups."
msgstr "Mengurangi latensi pada perangkat AMD Mesa yang didukung."

msgid "Use dGPU"
msgstr "Gunakan dGPU"

msgid "Makes the game use the AMD dGPU on hybrid systems."
msgstr "Membuat game menggunakan dGPU AMD pada sistem hybrid."

msgid "Hide AMD APU"
msgstr "Sembunyikan AMD APU"

msgid ""
"Makes Proton report an AMD APU as a discrete GPU for games that mis-detect "
"integrated graphics."
msgstr ""
"Membuat Proton melaporkan AMD APU sebagai GPU diskret untuk game yang salah "
"mendeteksi grafis terintegrasi."

msgid "NVAPI"
msgstr "NVAPI"

msgid "Lets games access NVIDIA-specific features like DLSS."
msgstr "Memungkinkan game mengakses fitur khusus NVIDIA seperti DLSS."

msgid "Update DLSS components"
msgstr "Perbarui komponen DLSS"

msgid "Auto upgrades DLSS components for supported games."
msgstr "Memperbarui komponen DLSS secara otomatis untuk game yang didukung."

msgid "Hide NVIDIA GPU"
msgstr "Sembunyikan GPU NVIDIA"

msgid ""
"Makes Proton report an NVIDIA GPU as AMD for games that expect Windows-only "
"NVIDIA driver behavior."
msgstr ""
"Membuat Proton melaporkan GPU NVIDIA sebagai AMD untuk game yang "
"mengharapkan perilaku driver NVIDIA khusus Windows."

msgid "AMD"
msgstr "AMD"

msgid "NVIDIA"
msgstr "NVIDIA"

msgid "GPU vendor options"
msgstr "Opsi vendor GPU"

msgid "Use GPU-specific compatibility toggles for AMD and NVIDIA hardware."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan pengalih kompatibilitas khusus GPU untuk perangkat keras AMD dan "
"NVIDIA."

#. More options
msgid "VKBasalt"
msgstr "VKBasalt"

msgid "Adds visual effects like sharpening and color adjustments."
msgstr "Menambahkan efek visual seperti penajaman dan penyesuaian warna."

msgid "WineD3D"
msgstr "WineD3D"

msgid ""
"Uses OpenGL instead of Vulkan. Only enable if you're having DXVK issues."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan OpenGL alih-alih Vulkan. Aktifkan hanya jika Anda mengalami "
"masalah DXVK."

msgid "More options"
msgstr "Opsi lainnya"

msgid "Extra graphics settings and launch behaviors."
msgstr "Pengaturan grafis ekstra dan perilaku peluncuran tambahan."

#. Game arguments
msgid "Skip launcher"
msgstr "Lewati peluncur"

msgid "Adds -skip-launcher to bypass launchers in games that support it."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan -skip-launcher untuk melewati peluncur pada game yang "
"mendukungnya."

msgid "Vulkan"
msgstr "Vulkan"

msgid "Adds -vulkan to make the game use its Vulkan renderer."
msgstr "Menambahkan -vulkan agar game menggunakan renderer Vulkan-nya."

msgid "DirectX 11"
msgstr "DirectX 11"

msgid "Adds -dx11 to make the game use its DirectX 11 renderer."
msgstr "Menambahkan -dx11 agar game menggunakan renderer DirectX 11-nya."

msgid "DirectX 12"
msgstr "DirectX 12"

msgid "Adds -dx12 to make the game use its DirectX 12 renderer."
msgstr "Menambahkan -dx12 agar game menggunakan renderer DirectX 12-nya."

msgid "Console"
msgstr "Konsol"

msgid "Adds -console to open the game's developer console when supported."
msgstr ""
"Menambahkan -console untuk membuka konsol pengembang game jika didukung."

msgid "Game arguments"
msgstr "Argumen game"

msgid "Flags passed directly to the game."
msgstr "Flag yang diteruskan langsung ke game."

#. Advanced options
msgid "Appends Steam's game command."
msgstr "Menambahkan perintah game Steam."

